{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"16de6104c1","title":"在汪东兴关于江西部分农村合作化发展情况报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"45a76a80e0","index":0,"year":1956,"month":2,"day":13,"articleId":"16de6104c1"}],"tags":[{"id":"3c11982f62","name":"汪东兴","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"9183cc5c53","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"汪东兴，当时任中共中央办公厅警卫局局长、公安部副部长。"},{"id":"53e9b9ad64","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指汪东兴1956年2月11日关于江西部分农村合作化发展情况给毛泽东的报告。报告说，据省委农村工作部统计，全省初级社入社农户已达总农户的78%。春耕前，群众结合搞生产规划，已在酰酿办高级社。有的地区已经铺开，计划今冬明春基本实现高级社。当前农村的主要问题是：抗水灾、早灾能力差，农用机器短缺，劳动力不足，牡畜、种子少，购买困难等。关于今后高级社的发展规划，省委打算分两步走（先试点，再扩大），但怕影响群众的积极性；如并作一步走，又担心工作缺乏经验，难以保证90%的社员增产。目前省委正在研究，还未作出定论。"},{"id":"50278c0429","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央副秘书长、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"cc92be5ff0","type":"title","text":"在江东兴“关于江西部分农村合作化发展情况报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1"},{"id":"9183cc5c53","type":"paragraph","text":"汪东兴的考察报告此件提出了一些问题，可以一阅。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1"},{"id":"53e9b9ad64","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1"},{"id":"50278c0429","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年二月十三日尚昆同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1"},{"id":"bf510add52","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请你印100份，发各政治局同志、农村工作部及中央警卫队约八十人，每人一份。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1"},{"id":"cef3f74b67","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1"},{"id":"14ef545124","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十三日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1"}],"page":{"id":"1356ab7e8d","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"16de6104c1","start":216,"end":217}}}},"__N_SSG":true}